# Portfolio Website — Project Overview

## Stack
- **Next.js 16** (App Router), **React 19**, **TypeScript 5** (strict mode)
- **Tailwind CSS 4** for styling, **next-themes** for dark mode
- **Vercel AI SDK** + **LangChain** + **AstraDB** for RAG-based chatbot
- **Resend** + **react-email** for contact form, **Zod** for validation
- **Upstash** for rate limiting

## Folder Structure
```
src/
  app/          # Next.js App Router pages + API routes + server actions
  components/   # Reusable components (ui/ for primitives, email/ for templates)
  lib/          # Shared utilities and external client setup (astra.ts, utils.ts)
  data/content/ # Plain-text files used as RAG knowledge base
  assets/       # Static images
  scripts/      # One-off scripts (data ingestion)
```

## General Rules
- Always use the `@/*` path alias for internal imports (never relative `../`)
- Keep pages in `app/`, shared UI in `components/`, helpers in `lib/`
- Never use `any` — use proper TypeScript types or generics
- No narrating code comments; only explain non-obvious intent or trade-offs
